file_name": "SS_Arcade.png", "id": "995616672152730", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974450_995616675486063_4244897958533011211_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=F_sF_PN3vZ4Q7kNvgFUTBOw&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDZWYZYJBl8L58a8Zkz9IHVeJXEDUoqrIugBDSfyTM43w&oe=6703DBE7"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CoverImage.png", "id": "362884679701179", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569444_362884683034512_8990070230059180269_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dLYsM7wG71sQ7kNvgEL0Z3B&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCM0R0ytUA-EyKyFGnNtVafMnpdiadlD_kPcHT3SdPlvg&oe=6703C3B6"}, "display_name": "Rage Against the Room", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to Rage Against the Room!  A VR rage room experience set in a satirical world where you find yourself inside a game show as the latest contestant looking at a chance of greatness!  Guiding you through will be the larger than life star of the show, Ryan the Rampage Rage, with his throat full of gravel chanting out while you rage.\n\nPlay through the story mode as convict made TV star, delving in to the behind the scene workings of the Rage Against the Room show.  Complete each of the rage arenas to further the story!\n\nAlternatively play the Arcade mode, allowing you to customise settings such as game length as well as respawning weapons and objects!\n\nEarn points through the Arcade game to unlock new weapons to spawn with!  Choose from weapons such as baseball bats, axes, wrenches, light tubes, crowbars, cleavers, lawn flamingos and more!", "short_description": "Rage Against the Room is here to allow to smash, crash and bash your way through all of our Ragerenas!  Use a variety of weapons and items to break down everything in your path and realise the key to unlocking your rage!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://freecreativ.com/pr